    <summary>
      Created ChatHistory component for displaying AI chat conversation:

      1. MESSAGE DISPLAY:
         - User messages right-aligned with brand background
         - Assistant messages left-aligned with neutral background
         - System messages centered with subtle styling
         - Role icons (Person for user, Bot for assistant)

      2. STYLING (ADR-021 COMPLIANT):
         - All colors use Fluent UI v9 tokens (no hard-coded values)
         - tokens.colorBrandBackground for user bubbles
         - tokens.colorNeutralBackground1 for assistant bubbles
         - tokens.colorNeutralBackground2 for container
         - Supports light/dark mode automatically

      3. AUTO-SCROLL:
         - useRef for message list container
         - useEffect triggers scroll on messages.length or isStreaming change
         - scrollTop = scrollHeight for smooth bottom anchoring

      4. OPERATION BADGES:
         - Fluent Badge component with color per operation type
         - add_node = success (green)
         - remove_node = danger (red)
         - update_node = warning (yellow)
         - add_edge = informative (blue)
         - remove_edge = subtle (gray)
         - Icons for each operation type

      5. STREAMING INDICATOR:
         - Spinner + text showing "AI is thinking..."
         - Displays current step and operation count
         - Uses streamingState from aiAssistantStore

      6. ACCESSIBILITY:
         - role="log" on container
         - role="list" on message list
         - role="listitem" on each message
         - aria-live="polite" for updates
         - aria-label on all major sections

      7. FILES MODIFIED:
         - components/AiAssistant/ChatHistory.tsx (275 lines)
         - components/AiAssistant/index.ts (added export)

      8. ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA MET:
